movies.Title: Ms. Marvel
movies.Actors: Iman Vellani, Matt Lintz, Zenobia Shroff
movies.Plot: Kamala, a superhero fan with an imagination--particularly when it comes to Captain Marvel--feels like she doesn't fit in at school and sometimes even at home, that is until she gets superpowers like the heroes she admires.
movies.Awards: Won 1 Primetime Emmy. 9 wins & 17 nominations total
